Package com.autopia4j.framework.webdriver.core

Core library of the autopia4j framework for Selenium WebDriver
This library is designed specifically for testing web applications (desktop as well as mobile), and integrates with Selenium WebDriver, Galen, Appium and Perfecto Mobile

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DriverScript
    Abstract class that defines the execution structure for data iteration based implementations of autopia4j
    ReusableLibrary
    Abstract base class for reusable libraries created by the user
    ScriptHelper
    Wrapper class for common framework objects, to be used across the entire test case and dependent libraries
    TestBatchHarness
    Singleton class that manages the result summary creation during a batch execution
    TestHarness  
    TestScript
    Abstract base class for test scripts developed using the autopia4j framework
    WebDriverTestParameters
    Class to encapsulate various input parameters required for each test script
    WebDriverTestParamsBuilder
    Builder class for the WebDriverTestParameters object
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Browser
    Enumeration to represent the browser to be used for execution
    DeviceType
    Enumeration to represent the type of device on which a test is executed
    ExecutionMode
    Enumeration to represent the mode of execution
